    {"type": "PostToolUseOutcome", "payload_shape": {"tool_call_id": "tcl_001", "tool_name": "get_weather", "outcome": "pass"}, "rationale": "Synthetic per §14.6.2; §15 post-hook result. OMITTED if adapter declares no hooks."},
